>> description: Fluffy pancakes on kefir
>> servings: 2

Pour @keffir{300%g} in a bowl.

Add @vanilin, @salt{1%g}, @sugar{15%g}, @egg{1%pc} to kefir. Mix everything.

Add @flour{200%g} and mix.

Add @soda and mix.

Heat #pan. Add @oil to fully cover surface

Pour dough with #ladle and fry until brown. Turn over with #spatula and fry on the other side

Add oil every time you fry new batch.

Serve with smetana or jam or condensed milk
